{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c9c3e3c781","title":"关于发表郭沫若访日诗篇的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"611e1acdf8","index":0,"year":1956,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"c9c3e3c781"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"f287104f71","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"郭沫若，当时任全国人大常委会副委员长、政协全国委员会副主席、中国科学院院长。"},{"id":"f23dcf4d88","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共北京市委第一书记、北京市市长。"},{"id":"79fdb153ad","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指信封内装的郭沫若访日诗篇七首。郭沫若于1955年12月1日至25日，应日本学术会议的邀请，率中国科学院学术考察团访问日本。这些诗是他访日期间写的。信封内的七首是：《箱根即景》《访须和田故居》《别须和田》《官岛即景》《访博多湾》《留别华侨》《游别府》。1956年2月29日在《北京日报》发表时，将《访博多湾》和《留别华侨》分别改题为《吊千代松原》和《归途在东海道车中》，又增加了《宿春帆楼》和《船入长江口》两首，这九首诗总题为《访日杂咏》"}],"contents":[{"id":"a456587366","type":"title","text":"关于发表郭沫若访日诗篇的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781"},{"id":"f287104f71","type":"paragraph","text":"送彭真同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781"},{"id":"f23dcf4d88","type":"paragraph","text":"内件以请交北京日报发表。其中有些草体字须先改为楷书，以免弄错。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781"},{"id":"79fdb153ad","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781"},{"id":"de83d11e20","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c9c3e3c781"}],"page":{"id":"fdcea7ce2e","publicationId":"maoquanji36